  m_text: "Now you have seen how well the methods have been developed. Are you satisfied
    with your results? If yes, Continue to Phase End Event where you must answer
    a series of questions based on these methods, otherwise you can take another
    round to re-invest and enhance the quality of the methods. \r\n\r\nDiscuss amongst
    all the colleagues and make a collective decision. The Master can choose the
    preferred option in the Game UI\r\n\r\nHint: If you are not confident about the
    quality of the methods you should reinvest again in the next round, but also
    take care of the timeline. You only have  8 rounds to complete the project. \r"
