  m_text: "Now you have seen how well the methods have been developed. Hopefully,
    you are satisfied with your results, because you are in the 8th and the last
    round of the game. So now, you can\u2019t spend another round investing in any
    of the phases again, that\u2019s why the \u201Creinvest in the next round button
    is disabled\u201D.\n\nThe users should now proceed to the phase end event and
    try to do with the best of their knowledge gained from developed methods. \n\nAre
    you satisfied with your results? You will find how you did after you complete
    the phase end event. All the Best!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
